Subject: [PATCH 2/9] dynamic loading of shared fdk-aac library

---
 configure                  |  5 +---
 libavcodec/libfdk-aacdec.c | 73 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--
 libavcodec/libfdk-aacenc.c | 59 +++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++--
